  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\">At the 3rd level, your aim with a sniper rifle becomes deadly. As a bonus action on your turn, you can overclock your targeting system to take careful aim at a creature you can see that is within range of a sniper rifle you're wielding. Your ranged attacks with the sniper rifle gain two benefits against the target:</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; padding-left: 1.4em; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">The attacks ignore half and three-quarters cover.</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\">On a hit, the weapon deals additional damage to the target equal to 2 + half your infiltrator level.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">This effect lasts 1 minute or until you use Steady Aim on a different target.</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">You can use this feature three times. You regain all expended uses of it when you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
